{"tid":2530733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呂秉權：料政府七一前有升級行動 或收回壹傳媒印刷廠房、辦公室、及要求交出任何被視為與危害國家安全有關新聞材料","createTime":"2021-05-14T15:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T16:35:27.000Z","uid":210495,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa69599e33df66e604c919f8c28422d2fbba2f0","tid":2530733,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T15:33:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210514/UZ6RQ55YIRFHVM3RAWALSFX4MQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210514%2FUZ6RQ55YIRFHVM3RAWALSFX4MQ%2F&d=z1Z9%2FhyuGVbDXJZ%2FGqhOoTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=fe8ea49f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210514%2FUZ6RQ55YIRFHVM3RAWALSFX4MQ%2F&h=cfedd65d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210514/UZ6RQ55YIRFHVM3RAWALSFX4MQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n呂秉權：相信當局不會對《蘋果》仁慈<br />\n浸大新聞系高級講師呂秉權接受《蘋果》訪問時形容，保安局的舉動是「拉人封艇」，他相信今次只是封殺壹傳媒的第一步，如果達不到停止《蘋果》運作的目的，當局仍會運用其他手段整頓壹傳媒，包括收回壹傳媒的印刷廠房及辦公室、要求集團交出任何被視為與危害國家安全有關的資料及新聞材料等。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到，港澳辦主任夏寶龍曾點名嚴懲黎智英，反映北京政府已將《蘋果日報》定性為政治集團，加上六四、七一等政治敏感日子臨近，特區政府某程度上要令社會局面更安寧。他稱若《蘋果》仍有一定影響力，相信當局不會對《蘋果》仁慈，七一前很可能會有升級行動。<br />\n<br />\n呂估計，黎智英及壹傳媒集團早已評估風險以制定應對措施，減低今次事件對集團運作的影響，當局亦應早已預視壹傳媒的部署，相信當局仍會有後着。"},{"pid":"14c006ce79b5941c780a1fd3a2b314a76def0aab","tid":2530733,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T16:21:27.000Z","msg":"想襟住<br />\n根住落黎既 64, 612, 616,626 既重溫報導/特刊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30fd99e014c9090637bcb774ef96191921544c8","tid":2530733,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T16:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9637e37b06e35e5151e5e58b1e701760892a75","tid":2530733,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T16:26:28.000Z","msg":"留港撚點應對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55272f38167a0c79078b597a2fa7d87adaf60e43","tid":2530733,"uid":325716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T16:35:27.000Z","msg":"唔係預咗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}